    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, but it's a bit broad. To really hit home with the voters, we need to be more specific about what we're fighting against. Can you add a section that explicitly calls out how these radical policies are actually harming children and why the progressive agenda is fundamentally a threat to the stability of the American home? Make it feel urgent.",
